1. *Konja* je ispašao iz štale. (The horse escaped from the stable.)
2. Stariji sin se vozio *konjom*. (The elder son was riding a horse.)
3. *Konjima* se hrani ovas. (The horses are fed oats.)
4. U selu ima puno *konja*. (There are a lot of horses in the village.)
5. Svi *konji* su bili veoma uzbuđeni. (All the horses were very excited.)
6. Ona je obukla svoje najlepše haljine da bi se vozila *konjem*. (She put on her prettiest dress to ride a horse.)